### 测试注册
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "张三",
  "username": "31250001",
  "password": "123456",
  "confirmPassword": "123456",
  "role": 1
}

### 学生登录（获取token）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "3125004123",
  "password": "123"
}

### 管理员登录（获取token）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "0025004123",
  "password": "123"
}

### 获取当前用户信息
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/info
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOjMsInJvbGUiOjEsImlhdCI6MTc3NDY2NDgyMSwiZXhwIjoxNzc0NzUxMjIxfQ.AC0sdXUlQl6KCOgdObDMiUpV0gNBxRrU63sCAF2DlpM

### 创建保修单（带图片）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/order/create
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOjMsInJvbGUiOjEsImlhdCI6MTc3NDY2NDgyMSwiZXhwIjoxNzc0NzUxMjIxfQ.AC0sdXUlQl6KCOgdObDMiUpV0gNBxRrU63sCAF2DlpM
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="deviceType"

空调
------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

不制冷
------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="priority"

2
------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="test.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary--


